<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>API documentation</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/docsPage.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>API documentation</h1>
    </header>
    <main class="Content">
        <li class="ListHead">
            GET /api/messages/list/{number}
            <ol class="ListItem">
                <p>Method for getting all messages with pagination by 10 messages per request.</p>
                <p>
                    <span style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-size: 20px;">number</span>
                    - Integer, number of page.
                </p>
                <p>In case of failure, returns following JSON object:</p>
                <ol>{"message":"error"}</ol>
                <p>Returning type: JSON object with the following structure:</p>
                <ol>
                    <p>"count" - Integer, total count of messages in database.</p>
                    <p>"currentCount" - Integer, count of messages on current page.</p>
                    <p>"messages" - array of objects Message from database.</p>
                </ol>
                <p>Examples:</p>
                <ol>
                    <p>/api/messages/list/0 - will return first 10 messages.</p>
                    <p>/api/messages/list/1 - will return second 10 messages.</p>
                    <p>etc.</p>
                </ol>
                <p>Result of /api/messages/list/2 :</p>
                <ol>
                    <pre>
{
    "data": {
        "count":21,
        "currentCount":1,
        "messages": [
            {
                "createdAt":"2021-01-30T14:05:51.712Z",
                "updatedAt":"2021-01-30T14:05:51.712Z",
                "_id":"6015683ffc2ecb2914b5b535",
                "authorName":"zxc",
                "authorEmail":"zxc@zxc.zxc",
                "messageText":"zxc",
                "__v":0
            }
        ]
    }
}
                    </pre>
                </ol>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li class="ListHead">
            GET /api/messages/single/{id}
            <ol class="ListItem">
                <p>Method for getting single message by unique identifier.</p>
                <p>
                    <span style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-size: 20px;">id</span>
                    - unique identifier of message in database.
                </p>
                <p>In case of failure, returns following JSON object:</p>
                <ol>{"message":"error"}</ol>
                <p>Returning type: JSON object Message from database.</p>
                <p>Example:</p>
                <ol>
                    <p>/api/messages/single/60141d6f06bfbc21d44bd104 - will return message with unique identifier 60141d6f06bfbc21d44bd104</p>
                    <ol>
                        <pre>
{
    "data": {
        "createdAt":"2021-01-29T14:36:06.791Z",
        "updatedAt":"2021-01-30T13:58:43.660Z",
        "_id":"60141d6f06bfbc21d44bd104",
        "authorName":"eeeeeef",
        "authorEmail":"kek@mail.com",
        "messageText":"lol",
        "__v":0
    }
}
                        </pre>
                    </ol>
                </ol>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li class="ListHead">
            POST /api/messages
            <ol class="ListItem">
                <p>Method for creating a new message.</p>
                <p>Body params:</p>
                <ol>
                    <p>nickname - String.</p>
                    <p>email - String.</p>
                    <p>message - String.</p>
                    <p>Fields createdAt and updatedAt are generated by Date.now()</p>
                </ol>
                <p>In case of failure, returns following JSON object:</p>
                <ol>{"message":"error"}</ol>
                <p>Returning type: JSON object Message from database. Returns created element.</p>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li class="ListHead">
            PUT /api/message
            <ol class="ListItem">
                <p>Method for message editing.</p>
                <p>Body params:</p>
                <ol>
                    <p>id - unique identifier of editing message.</p>
                    <p>nickname - String.</p>
                    <p>email - String.</p>
                    <p>message - String.</p>
                    <p>Field updatedAt are updated by Date.now()</p>
                    <p>Field createdAt remains unchanged.</p>
                </ol>
                <p>In case of failure, returns following JSON object:</p>
                <ol>{"message":"error"}</ol>
                <p>Returning type: JSON object Message from database. Returns new element.</p>
            </ol>
        </li>
        
    </main>
</body>
</html>